          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Project 4 -->
        <div class="project-row">
          <div class="project-left">
            <span class="project-number">04</span>
          </div>

          <div class="project-info">
            <h3 class="project-title">Chat Constellation</h3>

            <p class="project-desc">
              Created an AI chat interface that maps conversation threads into an interactive graph.
              Secured the app with JWT auth and backed conversations with MongoDB for session persistence.
            </p>

            <p class="project-tech">
              <span>Stack: </span>React <b>·</b> Node.js <b>·</b> Express <b>·</b> MongoDB <b>·</b> OpenAI API
            </p>

